data.name: CONVENTINAL BLOOD EXTRACTION NEEDLES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% medical grade stainless steel
- Polypropylene (PP) Needle Hub
- Isoprene Latex-Free Rubber Holder’s Needle’s Cover

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Color-Coded Size Identification

## PERFORMANCE
- 3 bevelled tip sharpness technology
- Air-Tight sealing with syringe’s tip
- Automatic Lubrication’s Technology => Optimal result on penetration resistance
- Thin wall technology => pressure reduction
